# Agency runtime secrets — loaded at startup via python-dotenv (Spec 331).
#
# Values are read from the SHELL ENVIRONMENT first (load_dotenv override=False).
# If a variable is already exported in your shell, this file is ignored for that
# key.  If not exported, the ${VAR} expansion resolves to empty string, which the
# drivers treat as "key not set" and degrade gracefully (no network call is made).
#
# To configure for local dev: export the keys in your shell, OR replace the
# ${VAR} expansions below with your actual values (never commit the filled-in copy).

JULES_API_KEY=${JULES_API_KEY}
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=${OPENROUTER_API_KEY}
AGENCY_LLM_MODEL=${AGENCY_LLM_MODEL}
